  • Use in commercial research and development
  • Integration into products for sale or distribution
  • Use in providing paid consulting or services

LICENSE REQUIREMENT:
Commercial use requires obtaining a separate Commercial License or SaaS License
from VINF-SJTU. Commercial licenses include:

  ✓ Full rights for commercial product development
  ✓ Open-source or closed-source plugin development support
  ✓ SaaS deployment authorization (with SaaS License)
  ✓ Technical support and updates
  ✓ Legal indemnification

